short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Translates all text on a page into Ubbi Dubbi.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: To Ubbi Dubbi will translate all text on a page into Ubbi Dubbi after the page has loaded. Because of this, results may not be consistent on dynamic websites or those that refresh content after page load. If you're in search of a great extension to install when a co-worker leaves his/her computer unlocked, look no further.
